[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.5,
    "text": "Good morning, Candace."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.5,
    "endTime": 3.84,
    "text": "What's so great about it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.84,
    "endTime": 4.8,
    "text": "Not much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.8,
    "endTime": 6.22,
    "text": "We can't find Perry anywhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.22,
    "endTime": 8.379999999999999,
    "text": "He's never missed breakfast, not even once."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.38,
    "endTime": 14.52,
    "text": "Uh, you don't think he could have argued with someone at, say, 338 AM, gone his feelings hurt, then run away, do you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.52,
    "endTime": 16.759999999999998,
    "text": "Nah, he never would have gone outside on purpose."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.76,
    "endTime": 19.98,
    "text": "Everybody knows platypuses are supposed to stay inside at night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.98,
    "endTime": 21.639,
    "text": "You haven't seen him anywhere, have you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.639,
    "endTime": 23.18,
    "text": "Well, maybe he just wandered off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.18,
    "endTime": 25.28,
    "text": "Doesn't he always wander off at some point in the day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.28,
    "endTime": 28.559,
    "text": "And then later, when he comes back, you say, oh, there you are, Perry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.639,
    "endTime": 30.139,
    "text": "And he says, brr."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.139,
    "endTime": 32.138999999999996,
    "text": "Yeah, but he's always here in the morning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.139,
    "endTime": 34.06,
    "text": "I'd be devastated if something happened to him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.06,
    "endTime": 34.86,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.86,
    "endTime": 35.599,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.599,
    "endTime": 36.4,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.4,
    "endTime": 37.199999999999996,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.2,
    "endTime": 38.02,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.02,
    "endTime": 38.82,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.82,
    "endTime": 39.619,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.619,
    "endTime": 41.4,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.4,
    "endTime": 45.4,
    "text": "Doofenshmirtz Evil Incorporated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.4,
    "endTime": 48.04,
    "text": "Hold on, I'm coming."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.04,
    "endTime": 49.82,
    "text": "Another gift basket?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.82,
    "endTime": 56.66,
    "text": "We regret to inform you that due to the regurgitator's recent evil behavior, you have been downgraded to a minor threat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.68,
    "endTime": 62.019999999999996,
    "text": "If you believe this to be a mistake, please fill out the included appeal for a minor threat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.02,
    "endTime": 63.779,
    "text": "Regurgitator?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.779,
    "endTime": 65.9,
    "text": "Oh, well, there's a lot of weirdos out there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.9,
    "endTime": 66.69900000000001,
    "text": "Oh, here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.699,
    "endTime": 67.82,
    "text": "He has his own blog."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.82,
    "endTime": 69.89999999999999,
    "text": "World's Most Evil Villain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.9,
    "endTime": 71.82000000000001,
    "text": "Who does this upstart think he is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.82,
    "endTime": 73.279,
    "text": "It's time to show him who's boss."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.279,
    "endTime": 78.419,
    "text": "All right, Ferb."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.419,
    "endTime": 80.75999999999999,
    "text": "Activate the Platitractor 3000."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.76,
    "endTime": 83.54,
    "text": "If Perry's anywhere in Danville, this will bring him home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.459,
    "endTime": 88.76,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.76,
    "endTime": 90.76,
    "text": "I didn't know there were so many platypuses in Danville."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.76,
    "endTime": 96.76,
    "text": "Yeesh, what a dump."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.76,
    "endTime": 100.26,
    "text": "Well, so much for Mr. Big Shot Supervillain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.26,
    "endTime": 101.55900000000001,
    "text": "Yeah, hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.559,
    "endTime": 104.559,
    "text": "I'm looking for someone named Mr. The Regurgitator."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.58,
    "endTime": 119.58,
    "text": "Hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.58,
    "endTime": 121.58,
    "text": "Do not push."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.58,
    "endTime": 122.08,
    "text": "Eh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.08,
    "endTime": 129.07999999999998,
    "text": "Oh, my Heinz Heine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.08,
    "endTime": 130.08,
    "text": "Look at this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.08,
    "endTime": 135.58,
    "text": "All this technology, a giant vacuum tube, and they can't afford a throw pillow?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.58,
    "endTime": 137.08,
    "text": "Oh, hello."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.08,
    "endTime": 139.08,
    "text": "I am the Regurgitator."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.58,
    "endTime": 145.58,
    "text": "Well, I guess I'll have to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.0,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "Well, OK, my name is Heinz Doofenshmirtz."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "Ta-da."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.0,
    "endTime": 153.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "I don't have the heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 157.0,
    "text": "Where are those lights coming from, by the way, when you do that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.0,
    "endTime": 159.0,
    "text": "You're that disturbed lunatic from Danville."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.0,
    "endTime": 160.5,
    "text": "Oh, you've heard of me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.5,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "Yes, and you've heard of me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 165.0,
    "text": "Seriously, where's that coming?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.0,
    "endTime": 167.0,
    "text": "Oh, look, you've already captured Perry the Platypus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.0,
    "endTime": 169.0,
    "text": "My, you do work fast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.0,
    "endTime": 172.5,
    "text": "Why don't you fill out these forms, and I'll consider you for a three-year internship."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.5,
    "endTime": 175.5,
    "text": "I am not here to apply for an internship."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.419,
    "endTime": 179.419,
    "text": "You can start by making a fresh pot of coffee."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.419,
    "endTime": 182.919,
    "text": "Nope, Ferb, not Perry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.919,
    "endTime": 186.419,
    "text": "This little guy's eyes are too close together, and his beak is orange."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.419,
    "endTime": 188.419,
    "text": "Perry's is more of a tangerine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.419,
    "endTime": 190.419,
    "text": "Nope, too fat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.419,
    "endTime": 191.419,
    "text": "Too thin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.419,
    "endTime": 193.419,
    "text": "Too cartoony."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.419,
    "endTime": 195.919,
    "text": "Whoa, that one smells like meatloaf."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.919,
    "endTime": 196.919,
    "text": "Perry!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.919,
    "endTime": 198.919,
    "text": "Perry the Platypus!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.919,
    "endTime": 199.919,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.919,
    "endTime": 200.919,
    "text": "Perry!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.919,
    "endTime": 201.919,
    "text": "Get over here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.919,
    "endTime": 204.419,
    "text": "You're coming home with me so I don't get in trouble with the..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.839,
    "endTime": 206.839,
    "text": "You have a pet beaver?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.839,
    "endTime": 208.839,
    "text": "You have a pet platypus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.839,
    "endTime": 210.839,
    "text": "Touche."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.839,
    "endTime": 212.339,
    "text": "Nope, too blue."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.339,
    "endTime": 213.839,
    "text": "Too angular."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.839,
    "endTime": 215.339,
    "text": "Too French."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.339,
    "endTime": 218.339,
    "text": "That one's just a duck with a beaver tail taped on him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.339,
    "endTime": 219.839,
    "text": "Well, that was the last of them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.839,
    "endTime": 221.839,
    "text": "Maybe we need to think bigger."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.839,
    "endTime": 222.839,
    "text": "And with music."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.839,
    "endTime": 224.839,
    "text": "Perry just loves music, remember?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.839,
    "endTime": 229.339,
    "text": "Let's get the guitars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.339,
    "endTime": 230.839,
    "text": "I've got an idea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.839,
    "endTime": 233.839,
    "text": "There's 104 days of summer vacation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.259,
    "endTime": 236.259,
    "text": "And the school comes along just to end it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.259,
    "endTime": 240.259,
    "text": " So the annual problem for our generation"
  }
]